task.summary: added sequencerEmpty (volatile to check # times sequencer has been emptied) added currentSampleRate (track's board's current true output rate) added check for sample rate defined by GS buffer. Overrides default sample rate changed threshold to 3/4s max DMA buffer size.
Added sample rate field that is checked by sequencer and allows on-the-fly clock rate changes Initial code to track current channel-values for optimization.
fixed unit test for multiple time points. - was writing same values to 5 channels multiple times, which is caught by new feature and throws assertion errors
